<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">I always get my characters, from level 5-6 to approximately 11 or 12, in Steamfont. From 1 to 5 too, depending on my starting location. The thing about Steamfont is that, like I wrote in another boast, it isn't static mobs (mostly) so you don't run out of them, you can kill a whole lot in a row before having to go far. From level 5 to 7, you can kill the kobolds like a machine for very good exp. After that eventually you keep killing stronger stuff when you're able to, like the pumas and skeletons. AAt level 10 you can go kill the mobs around the minotaur caves (personally I would just stand on the other side of the mountain close to the windmill, but that's just me). As usual, being twinked helps since we're far from being tanks. I soloed all my chars there, including my warrior.</FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#f7f5e6"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=1335"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Ibzi"></a>
